channel.title: Set xp?
channel.description:
okay i'm admin in a server and auto maxed right?
i'm not owner so i don't know how to un auto max.. i want 0 exp in all skills with still admin.. anyone know the code? i heard like ::setxp or something

item.title: Set xp?
item.dc:creator: @Colossus Colossus
item.description:
@Colossus wrote:

Some servers don’t have ::setxp for everyone, some servers have it for just the owner or if you’re 2 rights it may be for only people with the rights of 3.
but you could try doing ::setxp 00 00 all the way to ::setxp 20 00
